{"tid":192061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【伊院爆非禮案】24歲男護遭摸臀    警拘45歲印度男醫生","createTime":"2017-04-08T10:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T02:24:50.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7999ea8f2a2fb4051195a76bf391db67f311c516","tid":192061,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170408/large/1491645467_6098.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170408%2Flarge%2F1491645467_6098.jpg&h=32c639ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕涉嫌非禮24歲見習男護士的印度裔男醫生。<br />\n<br />\n公院接連再爆醜聞，伊利沙伯醫院今晨發生涉嫌非禮案！一名24歲見習男護士，今晨約7時半，報稱在更衣室內換衫其間，疑遭一名45歲印度裔來港交流的男醫生非禮。受害男護士隨即制止對方，並隨即向上級匯報事件，據知上級認為事態嚴重，遂報警求助。<br />\n警方經初步調查，得悉受害男護士一度遭人撫摸臀部，隨即以涉非禮將涉事印度裔男醫生拘捕，惟疑犯報稱不適，需要送院。"},{"pid":"92a2a30fd05da3697fd40d693eb3673a530ff6e5","tid":192061,"uid":84951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c069e75bd95045e19996ee00b4cfc9d5c5140a3d","tid":192061,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df47d32af676d9333d5b7a70af6c4e8a17dff696","tid":192061,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個醫生係港大出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印度裔來港交流的男醫生"},{"pid":"0a57a3c8d7da907389ea3ecbb733c130906d83f7","tid":192061,"uid":40624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t09rfK7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft09rfK7.jpg&h